OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment to overhaul drug
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpolicy to focus on getting 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fusers healthcare           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government will announce a new     
OL,6, drugs strategy on Monday overhauling   
OL,7, the drug recovery and treatment system,
OL,8, the BBC has learned.                   
OL,10,FThe announcement is expected to pledge 
OL,11,F#700m over three years to tackle       
OL,12,Fproblem drug use.                      
OL,14,FMeasures will include a large focus on 
OL,15,Fdiversion, a tactic designed to remove 
OL,16,Fdrug users from the criminal justice   
OL,17,Fsystem and get them into healthcare.   
OL,19,FMinisters are also set to announce     
OL,20,Finvestment to tackle drug gangs.       
